Detailed Description

template<int d, typename ct>
class Dune::SubYGrid< d, ct >::TransformingSubIterator

TransformingSubIterator is a SubIterator providing in addition a linear transformation of the coordinates of the grid in the form . This can be used to interpret the grid cells as vertices, edges, faces, etc.
